// Privacy
"about.privacy" = "Privacy Policy";
"privacy.title" = "Privacy Policy";
"privacy.done" = "Done";
"privacy.content" = "**MarkdownViewer** is a minimalist local Markdown editor. We take your privacy very seriously.

## Data Collection Statement

**MarkdownViewer does NOT collect any personal data.**

- **No Information Collection**: The app does not require user registration or login, and does not collect any personal information such as name, email, or location.
- **Local Processing**: All Markdown parsing, rendering, and storage are done locally on your device. Data is never uploaded to any server.
- **No Trackers**: The app does not contain any third-party SDKs, advertising plugins, or analytics tools.
- **File Access**: The current release is a non-sandboxed local tool. It reads Markdown and related same-directory resources only when you open a file.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via GitHub Issues.

---
*Last Updated: 2026-05-13*";

